  <h3>Step 3: Adjust for your spending profile</h3>
  <p>If you bought a new car this year, add $3,000–6,000 to your estimate. If you buy a lot of imported clothing or electronics, your number will be higher. If you mostly buy domestic goods and services, your number will be lower.</p>

